    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the cover (A). Remove the screw (B) and remove the HFT switch."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Installation Precautions"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. HFT switch Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2068_3.0_jpn_11389499_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Measure the resistance between the No. 2 and No. 3 terminals of the HFT switch 4P coupler in each position. If it is out of the standard value, replace the HFT switch."
